{"fadeType":1,"once":true,"scripts":[{"mode":1,"stopbgm":true,"sequence":[["梦幻的交汇\n\n<size=45>实现愿望的“神”<\/size>",1]]},{"flashout":{"dur":1,"alpha":[0,1],"black":true},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"无限的宇宙，无穷的次元，无数个世界……观测了那么多……","dir":1,"actorName":"观察者","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"actor":900012,"flashin":{"delay":1,"dur":1,"alpha":[1,0],"black":true},"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"挑出让人食指大动的世界，然后用值得参考的事物做了各种各样的试验呢","dir":1,"actorName":"测试者","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":900011,"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"只要用上镜面海域的话，大多事情都会变得混乱呢。之前在哪个宇宙的哪个星球来着不也观测到了吗？","dir":1,"actorName":"净化者","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":900021,"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"但是……只有这次的镜面海域的实验结果完全违背了我们的预期呢","dir":1,"actorName":"观察者","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":900012,"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"没想到本该由我们利用的世界会反过来利用了我们呢……","dir":1,"actorName":"测试者","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":900011,"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"也没这么严重吧？这次也就是“被猫抓了一下”这种程度吧？","dir":1,"actorName":"净化者","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":900021,"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"能影响我们的技术的存在，以及它的力量……那才是问题","dir":1,"actorName":"测试者","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":900011,"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"虽然不知道是什么人……不过那个世界里有着和中枢程序同等的，乃至更上级的存在","dir":1,"actorName":"观察者","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":900012,"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"？？？所以投影出的人偶们能装上舰装，能被强化也是那家伙搞的鬼咯","dir":1,"actorName":"净化者","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":900021,"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"不止如此……那个存在，居然还给我们写下了那种留言……","dir":1,"actorName":"测试者","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":900011,"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"那种台词……没有一定程度的自信可说不出来吧","dir":1,"actorName":"观察者","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":900012,"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"——你们的“愿望”是什么","dir":1,"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"“我会实现你们的愿望”…言外之意就是要我们付出相应的代价吧","dir":1,"actorName":"观察者","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":900012,"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"毫无代价就能实现的愿望自然不存在……不过根据人类的记录来看，不管是愿望还是代价通常都是很过分的东西呢","dir":1,"actorName":"测试者","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":900011,"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"不可承受之愿望之重……吗？基本都没什么好家伙呢","dir":1,"actorName":"净化者","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":900021,"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"那个存在要是实现了我们的愿望，那之后会让我们付出怎样的代价呢。不过很可惜……","dir":1,"actorName":"观察者","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":900012,"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"……","dir":1,"actorName":"测试者","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":900011,"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"我们不过是“程序”罢了——从一开始就不存在什么“愿望”啊。呵呵呵……","dir":1,"actorName":"观察者","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":900012,"blackBg":true}],"mode":2,"fadein":1.5,"id":"LINKPREHEAT17","fadeOut":1.5}